text: Nick Hits may refer to: *Nick Hits (Nickelodeon Latin America Block), a previous television block of Nickelodeon in Latin America. *Nick Hits (Netherlands & Flanders), a digital music television channel in The Netherlands & Flanders. On 1 February 2017 Nick Hits was rebranded by Nick Music. *Nick Hits, a streaming service available on Amazon Prime Video and Apple TV
title: Nick Hits
